In [72]:
#treating the missing values
cat=[]
con=[]
for i in df:
    if df[i].dtypes=='object':
        cat.append(i)
    else:
        con.append(i)
In [74]:
print(cat)
print(con)

['Province/State', 'Country/Region', 'Last Update']
['SNo', 'ObservationDate', 'Confirmed', 'Deaths', 'Recovered']
In [76]:
# for categorical column repace null values with mode
for i in cat:
    print(f"Modal value of {i} is {df[i].mode()[0]}")

Modal value of Province/State is Unknown
Modal value of Country/Region is Russia
Modal value of Last Update is 2021-04-02 15:13:53
In [78]:
#ffill up missing values fillna()

for i in df:
    if df[i].dtypes=='object':
        m=df[i].mode()[0]
        df[i]=df[i].fillna(m)
